Invocation Name: w. s. c. c. calendar
des: WSCC Calendar 2017-2018. Just say, "Alexa, ask w. s. c. c. calendar what is happening on September 10, 2017". You can also say, "Alexa, ask w. s. c. c. calendar what is happening in February 2018". If events are found, you can learn details of an event by asking with its event number. For example, to get details of event one, just say "tell me about event one".
